{"tid":25344,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"背光問題","createTime":"2016-12-06T05:25:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T15:12:58.000Z","uid":10420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c482521e2429051d99491f5b412d8e3025282f","tid":25344,"uid":10420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"想問問各位大師，<br />\n當你地去旅行乜野架餐都保無帶<br />\n得一機一鏡<br />\n<br />\n大晴天背光，影人+景<br />\n就得個背景正確曝光<br />\n就算開左機身閃光都無法為人樣補光<br />\n請問有無計呢？<br />\n定係要下下要後製？"},{"pid":"781210e687a018f4f570c38ebb9c5e766c945263","tid":25344,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:26:36.000Z","msg":"影raw輕輕一拉～<br />\n前提係你部機DR要闊<br />\ncanon機88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7e6d41e7e2676989a777392335788d870416a5","tid":25344,"uid":7955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:35:51.000Z","msg":"背景暗少少，機頭燈補少少主體。後制互相拉吓應該救到。正路背光，就要外閃嘅　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da983bfa7466d3d6c65998514ea66bf4ad870154","tid":25344,"uid":10420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:40:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>影raw輕輕一拉～<br />\n前提係你部機DR要闊<br />\ncanon機88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為我執相麻麻<br />\n同埋我用D610<br />\n個LR已經最新，但一入raw file <br />\n啲相會無哂機身調控效果<br />\n<br />\n加上我好少大執啲相<br />\n所以就好少影RAW<br />\n<br />\n睇黎都要習慣下影RAW"},{"pid":"fbb94a0052c9b01c71479abfe7d15c2a6eb4f130","tid":25344,"uid":10420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:45:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>背景暗少少，機頭燈補少少主體。後制互相拉吓應該救到。正路背光，就要外閃嘅　<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前去旅行會用相機背包<br />\n105 2.8 , 24-70 2.8  , 支閃用美斯58<br />\n但拎得好辛苦，又浪費左成個背包<br />\n<br />\n後來旅行想輕便，就只係帶支50 1.4<br />\n就咁用布袋包一包塞入袋<br />\n輕鬆好多玩得開心左<br />\n<br />\n但啲相就無咁靚囉"},{"pid":"f451c788606a282503efba1d2b1a0fb8ccd677ba","tid":25344,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>影raw輕輕一拉～<br />\n<br />\n前提係你部機DR要闊<br />\n<br />\ncanon機88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為我執相麻麻<br />\n<br />\n同埋我用D610<br />\n<br />\n個LR已經最新，但一入raw file <br />\n<br />\n啲相會無哂機身調控效果<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n加上我好少大執啲相<br />\n<br />\n所以就好少影RAW<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇黎都要習慣下影RAW</blockquote><br />\n你有時間可以睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zJOg_DdklwQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzJOg_DdklwQ&d=aISpdGVq1OuJ%2BcpSKkhvRQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=574f0475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zJOg_DdklwQ</a>"},{"pid":"39207b4268ca8809f0a2b0c8bf8fb7521813d1ed","tid":25344,"uid":12070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"耶穌應該唔會有背光問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ada586fbd896750a0dcc5222907d735840aa5c","tid":25344,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:12:58.000Z","msg":"求其執d 野當反光板用補補光"}]}